### Div

A generic `div` wrapper with custom class, id, or style. Uses triple-colon.

```
:::div[my-custom-class|my-id|color:red;font-size:1.2em]{
Content with custom styling applied.
}
```

- **`[class|id|style]`** — all optional, pipe-separated

#### Preview

:::div[my-custom-class|my-id|color:red;font-size:1.2em]{
Content with custom styling applied.
}